# OAuth/MSAL setup (both required):
# 1. Azure Portal > Entra ID > App registrations > New registration
# 2. Name: PRScope, Single tenant
# 3. Platform: SPA, Redirect URI: http://localhost:5173
# 4. API permissions > Add > APIs my org uses > "Azure DevOps" > Delegated > user_impersonation
# 5. Copy values below:
VITE_MSAL_CLIENT_ID=
VITE_MSAL_TENANT_ID=

# Fallback: PAT-based auth (no app registration needed)
# ADO_PAT=your-personal-access-token-here
